title: (Mon Part 1) Dolly Parton on Her Favorite Song to Perform + Final Round of BBS Theme Songs
itunes:title: (Mon Part 1) Dolly Parton on Her Favorite Song to Perform + Final Round of BBS Theme Songs
description:
We talk to the legend herself, Dolly Parton! Dolly tells us about her new book, favorite song to perform and what she does with her outfits after she wears them on stage/at big events. We listen to the final batch of theme songs submitted by listeners before we start voting on who will win the entire competition!
